Sample App: React To-Do List
Simple frontend app — React JS mein bani
User tasks add kar sakta hai, delete kar sakta hai
Isko Dockerize karna hai


Dockerfile banana:
Simple Dockerfile (Single-stage):



# Base image
FROM node:18-alpine

# Working directory
WORKDIR /app

# Dependencies copy karo
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm install

# Source code copy karo
COPY . .

# Build karo
RUN npm run build

# Port expose karo
EXPOSE 3000

# App chalao
CMD ["npm", "start"]

Problem: Is image ka size 500MB+ hota hai kyunki poora Node.js + build tools + source code sab included hai.
